to create database: 
go to external terminal -> sqlite3 <nameDB>
go to db manager class, run main, go to configuration then add the path of the db and "create" to the configuration field 
ex: \/home/studente/nameDB create
then run class dbmanager
To print db, go to configuration and write path db and a random string
ex: \/home/studente/nameDB 000

to connect db and server:
go to server main class -> configuration and add path of the db in configuration field
ex: \/home/studente/nameDB

then go in client and connect to db as normal
